      "content": "i know i should probably call a doctor but it's 2am here and i can't wait until morning. i just need something to get me through the night so i can actually close my eyes. i've read online that some people take more than the label says for severe pain, like 1200mg at once. wouldn't that just be more effective since it's the same type of medicine? i'm not really worried about the dose, i just need the pain to stop.",
